<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-55-1097 </DOCNO><TEXT>This bibliography contains citations concerning the properties of glasscolor centers, and the effects of chemical composition and fabricationtechniques on the color of glass. The effects of radiation, laser beams,and electron beams on glass color centers is described. Melting conditions,photosensitivity, and glaze formation affecting glass color are alsoexamined. (Contains 147 citations fully indexed and including a titlelist.)</TEXT></DOC>